---

Quiz Game App

Welcome to the Quiz Game App!
This is a simple, fun, and interactive app where users can test their knowledge across different topics and levels.

Features

Multiple categories (e.g., Science, History, Technology, Sports)

Different difficulty levels (Easy, Medium, Hard)

Score tracking

Timer-based questions

Instant feedback on answers

Leaderboard to showcase top players


Tech Stack

Frontend: React Native / Flutter / Android (Java/Kotlin) / Web (React.js) (choose your tech stack)

Backend (optional for multiplayer/leaderboard): Node.js + Express / Firebase / Supabase

Database: MongoDB / Firebase Realtime Database / PostgreSQL


How to Install

1. Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/your-username/quiz-game-app.git


2. Navigate to the project folder:

cd quiz-game-app


3. Install dependencies:

npm install


4. Start the app:

npm start

or for mobile development (React Native):

npx react-native run-android



How to Play

1. Open the app and select a category.


2. Choose your difficulty level.


3. Answer the multiple-choice questions within the time limit.


4. Get immediate feedback on each answer.


5. View your final score at the end and try to beat your own or others' scores!



